7 Mitchell Place (East 49th Street), adjoining the N.E. corner of First Ave., as seen across the clearance at the corner, upon which was constructed the 26-story Pan Hellenic House. Also shown is the west wall of the partially completed Stewart Hall (No. 10 Mitchell Place). This set consists of a negative and a positive.

October 28, 1927.

F. M. Demarest.
Gift of Albert A. Volk Co.

Mitchell Place, (north side of East 49th Street), north side, east from and including First Ave., to Beekman place.

September 20, 1927.

P. L. Sperr.
